/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n舊式公屋 一定冇人彩你放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f747b4f3642f5dcc8f4a28053e6bd07473539bf","tid":56074,"uid":6702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:29:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咩途徑可以投訴佢地等佢地無得養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n舊式公屋 一定冇人彩你放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁日日繼續比狗吠"},{"pid":"f3fbbccf026117a084835bd8474f3c5afed2feb1","tid":56074,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:30:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3566ad47560e49c548f3e174081d90be4cb22e8b","tid":56074,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>養狗有咩問題？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n養寵物係非必要開支<br />\n<br />\n其次係而家公屋已經唔比養, 理論上舊批准死左既就唔可以再養</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開唔開支都次要，下面所有圓柱體既物體都有尿蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早兩日先投訴完一個"},{"pid":"ce809d2b95a0ec90426ca664244d1fca7ccd53d1","tid":56074,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>養狗即係有閒錢<br />\n<br />\n有閒錢即係冇經濟負擔<br />\n<br />\n冇經濟負擔即係冇住公屋需要<br />\n<br />\n咁就讓撚返間公屋出黎啦 屌公屋養狗班人老母臭閪</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有千零蚊閒錢出面都租唔到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隻狗有咩病醫藥費閒閒地都幾千幾萬<br />\n細病皮膚病都可以八百至一千蚊左右<br />\n仲撚貴過人<br />\n<br />\n住公屋需要係邊"},{"pid":"44b19c67792e25e8dd6663315809b022532675ba","tid":56074,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:36:23.000Z